from one language to another.

00:03:42.910 --> 00:03:45.420 align:middle line:84%
It's a kind of bridge
language, whereby

00:03:45.420 --> 00:03:47.910 align:middle line:84%
the language of an
original document

00:03:47.910 --> 00:03:51.330 align:middle line:84%
can be translated
