from scratch thousands of years

00:04:01.740 --> 00:04:05.850 align:middle line:84%
ago and in one of the most
remote regions of the world?

00:04:05.850 --> 00:04:10.720 align:middle line:90%


00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:14.560 align:middle line:84%
To answer this, we need
to look at the Aymara

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:16.329 align:middle line:90%
people themselves.

00:04:16.329 --> 00:04:18.880 align:middle line:84%
And they are one of
the oldest on Earth.

00:04:18.880 --> 00:04:21.279 align:middle line:84%
And even so, they
are the progeny

00:04:21.279 --> 00:04:25.720 align:middle line:84%
of an even older culture, the
Bukidnon, whose tribespeople

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:29.230 align:middle line:84%
