seeding of knowledge

00:42:09.980 --> 00:42:12.770 align:middle line:84%
around the world by
the gods themselves,

00:42:12.770 --> 00:42:15.860 align:middle line:84%
in what seems to have been a
carefully orchestrated plan

00:42:15.860 --> 00:42:19.590 align:middle line:84%
to assist hunter
gatherers gradually evolve

00:42:19.590 --> 00:42:23.360 align:middle line:90%
towards a more civilized state.

00:42:23.360 --> 00:42:26.030 align:middle line:84%
And too many traditions
